content: {"name": "Betsy and Peter Fischer Food Pantry (Samost Jewish Family & Children's Service of SNJ)", "alternate_name": "", "description": "* If you are new to JFCS and need food assistance, please call (856) 424-1333 or email faphelp@jfedsnj.org to schedule a confidential intake appointment.\n\n* JFCS provides monthly distributions of kosher, non-perishable food, household essentials, and personal care items to food-insecure residents of Camden, Burlington, and Gloucester Counties", "email": "", "url": "https://jfcssnj.org/pantry-assistance-requests/", "status": "active", "address": {"address_1": "6 East Miami Avenue", "address_2": null, "city": "Cherry Hill", "state_province": "NJ", "postal_code": "08034", "country": "US"}, "location": {"latitude": 39.9182218, "longitude": -75.00509360000001}, "phones": [{"number": "(856) 751-9500", "type": "voice"}], "regular_schedule": [{"weekday": "Monday", "opens_at": "13:00", "closes_at": "19:00"}, {"weekday": "Tuesday", "opens_at": "13:00", "closes_at": "19:00"}, {"weekday": "Wednesday", "opens_at": "13:00", "closes_at": "19:00"}], "service_attributes": [{"attribute_key": "REQUIREMENT", "attribute_value": "Call in advance for services"}, {"attribute_key": "REQUIREMENT", "attribute_value": "Appointments required"}]}
